for example use :

1. To Login:
    >>> tg login --phone <yourPhone>

Remember after you logged in a file in directory "conn" will be created. Every time you want
to call other commands you must enter flag: --phone <yourPhone>

2. To Get Updates:
    >>> tg getUpdates --phone <yourPhone> --numberOfUpdates <n> --minutes <m>

3. To Get History
    >>> tg getHistory --phone <yourPhone> --peerID <x> --peerAccessHash <h>

